    <item>
      <title>BOJ观察者看到逐率越来越高的终端速率远足</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/boj-watchers-see-gradual-rate-hikes-with-higher-terminal-rate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据最新的彭博社调查，日本守望者仍然期望利率上升的速度会逐渐增加，尽管他们现在看到当前周期的利率上升到更高的水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-12/boj-watchers-see-gradual-rate-hikes-with-higher-terminal-rate</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 00:15:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
